esidents of the heavens and the earth. Nothing shall hinder you from anything else. There is no God but You! You have power over all things.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ مِنْكَ اِلَيْكَ اَفِرُّ وَلَيْسَ ذٰلِكَ اِلَّا مِنْ خَوْفِيْ عَدْلَكَ وَاِيَّاكَ اَسْئَلُ بِكَ لِاَنَّهٗ لَيْسَ اَحَدٌ اِلَّا دُوْنَكَ وَلَا اَقْدِرُ اَنْ اَسْتَتِرَ مِنْكَ فِيْ لَيْلٍ وَلَا نَهَارٍ وَاَنَا عَارِفٌ بِرُبُوْبِيَّتِكَ مُقِرٌّ بِوَحْدَانِيَّتِكَ اَحَطْتَ يَا اِلٰهِيْ خُبْرًا بِاَهْلِ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَاَهْلِ الْاَرْضِ لَا يَشْغَلُكَ شَيْ‌ءٌ عَنْ شَيْ‌ءٍ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اَنْتَ‌ اِنَّكَ عَلٰى‌ كُلِّ شَيْ‌ءٍ قَدِيْرٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedS